\c 30 30 1 Shoko raJehovha rakasvikazve kwandiri, richiti, 2 "Mwanako‑ mana womunhu, porofita, uti, zvanzi naIshe 3ehovha, `Ungudzai! Aiwa, zuva rakaipa sei!' 3 Nokuti zuva rava pedyo, izuva ramakore; ichava nguva yamarudzi avanhu. 4 Munondo uchauya pamu‑ soro peIjipiti, kurwadziwa kukuru ku‑ chavapo paItiopia, kana vakaurawa
